92
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,260
Je suis toi.

93
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,570
Tu es moi.

94
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,660
Nous

95
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:16,060
